org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IFileNodeAccumulator

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileNode, FXGFileNode, MXMLFileNode, ResourceBundleFileNode

    public interface IFileNodeAccumulator
    Any nodes/information which are to be collected during parsing and stored on the FileNode should be added to this interface.
